title: Harju JK Laagri
text: Harju JK Laagri is a soccer team of <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club Harju Jalgpallikool, based in <a href="Laagri">Laagri</a>, <a href="Harjumaa">Harjumaa</a>. Founded in 2009, they currently play in the <a href="II%20Liiga">II Liiga</a>, the fourth tier of Estonian football.
